SUMMARY:RVSHC Second Chance Prom
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T180000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T230000
UID:056161408dc655ca490a02c48004eb51@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Glam & Fun - Fostering Communication and Connection Get ready 
 to SPARKLE! Whether you missed your high school prom\, want to relive the 
 magic\, or just need an excuse to get glammed up\, this is your night to s
 hine AND show up for your community. Join us for a sophisticated "second c
 hance" at the ultimate prom experience featuring an evening of glitz\, gla
 mour\, dancing\, and memories to last a lifetime. For over 60 years\, The 
 Roanoke Valley Speech and Hearing Center has been helping people of all ag
 es better relate to the world around them. We are excited to present our v
 ery first Second Chance Prom Fundraiser - a charity gala supporting our mi
 ssion to improve quality of life through effective communication.
URL:https://business.roanokechamber.org/events/details/rvshc-second-chance
 -prom
