SUMMARY:Explore Spiritual Freedom with Eckankar at the 2026 Festival of Li
 ght!
DESCRIPTION:Roanoke Spiritual Experiences Group\nLocation:\nBoonsboro Ruri
 tan Club\n1499 Coffee Road\nLynchburg VA 24503\nDescription:\nAre you read
 y to enhance your spiritual journey or curious about reincarnation? Learn 
 how to find divine love in everyday life and explore the special connectio
 n you have with your pet\, because animals are Soul too! Visit us at the E
 CKANKAR Booth to share stories of love and coincidences\, learn about the 
 spiritual benefits of the ancient teachings of ECKANKAR\, the Path of Spir
 itual Freedom\, and discuss your favorite animals and their spiritual sign
 ificance. Take a spin on the ECK Wisdom Wheel to see what divine message c
 omes through for you.\nA flyer for this event is available at:\n[https://e
 ck-va.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/L-Burg-Poster-Spring-Festival-of-Ligh
 t-021526.pdf](https://eck-va.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/L-Burg-Poster-
 Spring-Festival-of-Light-021526.pdf)
