BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Taubman Museum": "https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/event/garden-sculpture-workshop-with-artist-larry-bechtel-part-2/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:taubman_museum
SUMMARY:Garden Sculpture Workshop with Artist Larry Bechtel - Part II
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T153000
UID:10001953-1774184400-1774193400@www.taubmanmuseum.org
DESCRIPTION:Nancy Lorenz: The Elements Does your garden\, yard\, or window
  box need a little surprise\, something to peek out from under your flower
 s and bring a smile to anybody who comes by? If so\, we invite you to sign
  up for Larry Bechtel’s newest sculpture class and make a concrete garde
 n face (about 6″ high and 4-5″ inches wide)! This will be a fun projec
 t\, but you will also learn three sculpting skills: modeling a face in cla
 y\, molding this in plaster\, and casting a concrete copy from the plaster
  mold. No experience is necessary. All materials will be provided. Please 
 note that samples pictured are only for inspiration – individual class p
 rojects will vary depending on students’ creative visions. Two sessions 
 are included for the price of one! PART I – Sunday\, March 15\, 1-3:30 P
 M PART II – Sunday\, March 22\, 1-3:30 PM Price for both sessions: Membe
 rs: $150 | General Public: $175 Add to Calendar Driving? Get Directions Sh
 are This! Register Now Date: Feb 04\, 2027 May 16\, 2027\n\nSource: https:
 //www.taubmanmuseum.org/event/garden-sculpture-workshop-with-artist-larry-
 bechtel-part-2/
LOCATION:Taubman Museum of Art\, 110 Salem Ave SE\, Roanoke\, VA\, 24011\,
  United States
URL:https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/event/garden-sculpture-workshop-with-art
 ist-larry-bechtel-part-2/
X-SOURCE:Taubman Museum of Art
END:VEVENT
