UID:068300a6a90505c29ed4e2ea2cec0e59@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Healthcare is a critical pillar of our regional economy and qu
 ality of life. Join the Roanoke Regional Chamber for our first installment
  of the VBR Series presented by inFirst Credit Union: State of Healthcare 
 presented by Anthem\, a morning program designed to provide insight into t
 he trends\, challenges\, and innovations shaping healthcare across Virgini
 a’s Blue Ridge. This event will feature updates from two of the region
 ’s leading healthcare organizations: Carilion Clinic and LewisGale Medic
 al Center. Representing Carilion Clinic\, President of Carilion Medical Ce
 nter\, Mike Abbott will share insights into the current healthcare landsca
 pe\, highlight key initiatives and special projects\, and discuss what lie
 s ahead for the region. Additional speaker details from LewisGale Medical 
 Center will be announced soon. Attendees will gain a clearer understanding
  of how regional healthcare systems are evolving\, the investments being m
 ade locally\, and the role healthcare plays in driving economic v
URL:https://business.roanokechamber.org/events/details/2026-state-of-healt
 hcare
X-SOURCE:Roanoke Regional Chamber
END:VEVENT
