SUMMARY:Mixed Media Face Cards Class
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T123000
UID:10001956-1774693800-1774701000@www.taubmanmuseum.org
DESCRIPTION:Nancy Lorenz: The Elements Turn ordinary playing cards into ex
 traordinary miniature artworks in this creative mixed-media class! Using f
 ace cards as your canvas\, you’ll design and embellish a one-of-a-kind k
 eepsake inspired by either a beach or garden theme. Learn how to layer “
 bits and bobs” like beads\, ribbon\, wire\, charms\, and tiny miniatures
  to add texture\, dimension\, and personality to your piece. Leave with a 
 beautifully finished keepsake ready to hang or display\, and the skills to
  create more at home! Please note that the sample image shows examples of 
 cards created by the instructor. Cards created in class will differ in sty
 le and theme. Registration required. Members: $20 | General Public: $25 No
 t a Member? Join today and receive discounts on classes and camps\, exclus
 ive invites to events\, and FREE reciprocal membership to the Virginia Mus
 eum of Fine Arts in Richmond\, among other perks! Click here to learn more
  and join. Add to Calendar Driving? Get Directions Share This! Register No
 w Date: Feb 04\, 2027 May 16\, 2027\n\nSource: https://www.taubmanmuseum.o
 rg/mixed-media-playing-cards
LOCATION:Taubman Museum of Art\, 110 Salem Ave SE\, Roanoke\, VA\, 24011\,
  United States
