SUMMARY:Haydn: The Glory of the Natural Horn
DESCRIPTION:Revel in the power\, precision\, and poetry of this rare musical experience.\nJoin David Stewart Wiley and our new RSO Principal Horn Christopher Caudill and his wife Rachel Niketopoulos in an evening that showcases the brilliance and beauty of the natural horn.  We will feature both Beethoven and Telemann concerto’s with amazing virtuoso displays on period horn instruments. \nThanks to our Sponsor!
