DESCRIPTION:The Roanoke Valley Spring Home Show (SHS)\, hosted by the Roan
 oke Regional Home Builders Association\, which includes many members of th
 e Roanoke Regional Chamber\, is returning for its 54th year as the longest
 -running and only locally operated home show in our region. This premier e
 vent connects builders\, contractors\, and home industry professionals dir
 ectly with homeowners ready to build\, renovate\, and invest. Interested i
 n becoming an exhibitor or vendor? Contact Amy Lowman\, Executive Officer 
 of the RRHBA\, at alowman@rrhba.com or visit thespringhomeshow.com for mor
 e details.
