URL:https://www.roanokeva.gov/calendar.aspx?EID=8606
DESCRIPTION:The Foot Levelers Blue Ridge Marathon is the premier running e
 vent in the Roanoke Valley. It showcases our region to runners across the
  country and the globe and has created a multi-million dollar economic im
 pact for the region over the past 17 years. Festivities start with packet
  pickup and a concert on Friday evening in Elmwood Park\, continue on Sat
 urday with the main event - a 26.2 mile foot race that goes up Mill Mount
 ain\, to the Blue Ridge Parkway\, \nback into the city to Mill Mountain S
 tar\, through neighborhoods\, and finishing in Elmwood Park. A concert fo
 llows in the evening\, and the weekend is wrapped up on Sunday with the "
 Slow-K" 5K event on the greenway. https://www.roanokeva.gov/calendar.aspx
 ?EID=8606
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE:20260419
DTSTAMP;TZID=America/New_York:20251229T134859
