DESCRIPTION:✂️ Upcoming Ribbon Cutting: Ronald McDonald House of South
 west Virginia ✂️ Please join us for an upcoming ribbon cutting celebra
 ting Ronald McDonald House! ✂️❤️ We’re honored to celebrate Rona
 ld McDonald House and the incredible support they provide to families duri
 ng some of life’s most challenging moments. This ribbon cutting is a mea
 ningful opportunity to recognize their impact\, thank their team and suppo
 rters\, and show our community’s appreciation for the work they do every
  day. Their House is a home-away-from-home where families can stay close\,
  close to the care and resources they need\, close to each other\, and clo
 se to their child while they are in the hospital. They provide an inviting
  resting place for families that need to stay overnight\, as well as the R
 onald McDonald Family Room on the 14th floor of Carilion Children's Hospit
 al for those who need a break without leaving the hospital. We hope you’
 ll join us as we help mark this special moment and celebrate an organizati
 on tha
