SUMMARY:Greenway Litter Pickup
DESCRIPTION:Pathfinders For Greenways\nPlease join us for our monthly litt
 er pick-up on the Roanoke Valley greenways!\n\nThis month\, we will pick-u
 p litter along the --- in ---.\n\nIf you are not available this month\, we
  meet the first Thursday morning of the month for future litter pick-up ev
 ents.\n\nDate: Thursday\, ---\, 2026\nTime: 7:30 am-9:00 am\nLocation: TBD
 \nGoogle Directions: ---\n\nGPS Coordinates: ---\n\nWhat to bring/wear:\nC
 omfortable\, closed toe shoes\nLong pants\nHi-Viz vest/shirt (if available
  - we will be working near traffic along the greenway)\nSafety glasses (if
  available)\nHat\, sunscreen\, sunglasses\, etc.\nWater bottle\nDisposable
  gloves and trash bags will be provided.\nThank you for your support to he
 lp maintain our greenways!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pathfinders-for-greenways/events/3122
 80300/
