DESCRIPTION:Pathfinders For Greenways\nPlease join us for our monthly litt
 er pick-up on the Roanoke Valley greenways!\n\nThis month\, we will pick-u
 p litter along the --- in ---.\n\nIf you are not available this month\, we
  meet the first Thursday morning of the month for future litter pick-up ev
 ents.\n\nDate: Thursday\, ---\, 2026\nTime: 9:00 am-10:30 am\nLocation: TB
 D\nGoogle Directions: ---\n\nGPS Coordinates: ---\n\nWhat to bring/wear:\n
 Comfortable\, closed toe shoes\nLong pants\nHi-Viz vest/shirt (if availabl
 e - we will be working near traffic along the greenway)\nSafety glasses (i
 f available)\nHat\, sunscreen\, sunglasses\, etc.\nWater bottle\nDisposabl
 e gloves and trash bags will be provided.\nThank you for your support to h
 elp maintain our greenways!
